# EmailJS configuration for the Contact form
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.emailjs.com
# 2. Add an Email Service (e.g. Gmail) -> copy its "Service ID"
# 3. Create an Email Template with {{name}}, {{email}}, {{message}} variables -> copy its "Template ID"
# 4. Go to Account > General -> copy your "Public Key"
# 5. Copy this file to ".env" (not .env.example) and fill in the real values below
# 6. Never commit the real .env file - it's already ignored in .gitignore

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
